[{"text": "I want you now to imagine", "start": 15.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a wearable robot", "start": 18.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that gives you superhuman abilities,", "start": 21.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "or another one that takes wheelchair users", "start": 25.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "up standing and walking again.", "start": 29.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We at Berkeley Bionics", "start": 33.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "call these robots exoskeletons.", "start": 36.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "These are nothing else", "start": 40.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "than something that you put on in the morning,", "start": 42.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it will give you extra strength,", "start": 45.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it will further enhance your speed,", "start": 48.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and it will help you, for instance, to manage your balance.", "start": 52.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "It is actually the true integration", "start": 56.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "of the man and the machine.", "start": 60.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But not only that --", "start": 62.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it will integrate and network you", "start": 64.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to the universe", "start": 66.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and other devices out there.", "start": 68.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is just not some blue sky thinking.", "start": 70.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "To show you now what we are working on", "start": 73.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "by starting out talking about", "start": 76.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the American soldier,", "start": 78.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that on average does carry about 100 lbs. on their backs,", "start": 80.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and they are being asked to carry more equipment.", "start": 84.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Obviously, this is resulting", "start": 87.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in some major complications --", "start": 90.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "back injuries, 30 percent of them --", "start": 92.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "chronic back injuries.", "start": 96.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So we thought we would look at this challenge", "start": 98.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and create an exoskeleton", "start": 101.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that would help deal with this issue.", "start": 104.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "So let me now introduce to you HULC --", "start": 108.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "or the Human Universal", "start": 112.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Load Carrier.", "start": 114.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Soldier: With the HULC exoskeleton,", "start": 117.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I can carry 200 lbs. over varied terrain", "start": 119.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for many hours.", "start": 121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Its flexible design allows for deep squats,", "start": 123.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "crawls and high-agility movements.", "start": 125.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It senses what I want to do, where I want to go,", "start": 128.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and then augments my strength and endurance.", "start": 131.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Eythor Bender: We are ready with our industry partner", "start": 137.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to introduce this device,", "start": 140.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "this new exoskeleton this year.", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So this is for real.", "start": 145.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Now let's turn our heads", "start": 147.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "towards the wheelchair users,", "start": 150.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "something that I'm particularly passionate about.", "start": 153.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There are 68 million people", "start": 156.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "estimated to be in wheelchairs worldwide.", "start": 158.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is about one percent of the total population.", "start": 161.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And that's actually a conservative estimate.", "start": 164.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We are talking here about, oftentimes,", "start": 167.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "very young individuals with spinal cord injuries,", "start": 169.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that in the prime of their life -- 20s, 30s, 40s --", "start": 172.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "hit a wall", "start": 175.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the wheelchair's the only option.", "start": 177.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But it is also the aging population", "start": 179.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that is multiplying in numbers.", "start": 181.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And the only option, pretty much --", "start": 184.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "when it's stroke or other complications --", "start": 187.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is the wheelchair.", "start": 189.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And that is actually for the last 500 years,", "start": 191.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "since its very successful introduction, I must say.", "start": 195.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So we thought we would start", "start": 199.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "writing a brand new chapter", "start": 201.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of mobility.", "start": 204.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Let me now introduce you to eLEGS", "start": 207.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that is worn by Amanda Boxtel", "start": 210.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "that 19 years ago was spinal cord injured,", "start": 214.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and as a result of that", "start": 218.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "she has not been able to walk", "start": 220.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for 19 years until now.", "start": 222.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 225.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Amanda Boxtel: Thank you.", "start": 228.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 230.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "EB: Amanda is wearing our eLEGS set.", "start": 235.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "It has sensors.", "start": 239.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's completely non-invasive,", "start": 242.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "sensors in the crutches", "start": 244.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that send signals back to our onboard computer", "start": 246.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that is sitting here at her back.", "start": 249.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There are battery packs here as well", "start": 252.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that power motors that are sitting at her hips,", "start": 254.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as well as her knee joints,", "start": 257.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that move her forward", "start": 259.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in this kind of smooth and very natural gait.", "start": 261.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "AB: I was 24 years old", "start": 268.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and at the top of my game", "start": 270.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when a freak summersault while downhill skiing", "start": 272.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "paralyzed me.", "start": 275.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In a split second,", "start": 277.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I lost all sensation and movement", "start": 279.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "below my pelvis.", "start": 282.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Not long afterwards,", "start": 285.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a doctor strode into my hospital room,", "start": 287.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and he said, \"Amanda,", "start": 290.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you'll never walk again.\"", "start": 292.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "And that was 19 yeas ago.", "start": 296.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "He robbed", "start": 299.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "every ounce of hope", "start": 301.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from my being.", "start": 303.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Adaptive technology", "start": 305.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "has since enabled me", "start": 307.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to learn how to downhill ski again,", "start": 309.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to rock climb and even handcycle.", "start": 311.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But nothing has been invented", "start": 314.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "that enables me to walk,", "start": 318.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "until now.", "start": 320.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 322.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 325.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 327.26, "duration": 8.0}, {"text": "EB: As you can see,", "start": 335.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have the technology,", "start": 337.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have the platforms", "start": 339.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to sit down and have discussions with you.", "start": 341.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It's in our hands,", "start": 344.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we have all the potential here", "start": 346.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "to change the lives", "start": 350.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of future generations --", "start": 352.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not only for the soldiers,", "start": 354.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "or for Amanda here and all the wheelchair users,", "start": 358.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "but for everyone.", "start": 362.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "AB: Thanks.", "start": 364.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 366.26, "duration": 11.0}]